name: Femi's Army: Meeting of the Mountain Men
description:
This was not an impressive expedition.
The men with scars looked on and stared.
Who was this great man they spoke of?
And why were they scared?
On a normal occasion they would beat them.
Steal and plunder.
Brawl and fight.
But this time they were forewarned to bring only a message.
To come together.
To unite.
And so they whispered instruction.
Told no more than what they were to do.
They had no idea of the meaning.
Nor did they care to.
